JoliCode is a French company based in Paris, with a high level of expertise in developing high quality web and mobile projects. Our goal is to help improve the level of quality of the Web and mobile projects of our clients.

Our main domains of expertise include :

Audit and consulting: we help our clients in fixing architecture problems or performance, scalability and platform optimization issues, and can run mobile application or website audits;
Architecture and expertise: we can deliver team support/coaching during projects initialization or later in projects lifecycles, from an organizational or purely technical perspective;
Development: we can build ourselves your whole stacks, from the technical specifications to the production;
Training courses: we offer trainings for all the technologies we use in our projects like PHP, Symfony, Elasticsearch, Appcelerator Titanium, JavaScript, Docker,...

